com.github.i49.hibiscus.schema

Interface Property


  • public interface Property
    A property or field which is a name-value pair composing an ObjectType.

    An instance of this type can be created through SchemaComponents.required(), SchemaComponents.optional(), or SchemaComponents.pattern()

    
 import static com.github.i49.hibiscus.schema.SchemaComponents.*;
 Property p = required("name", string());
    See Also:
    SchemaComponents
